classDiagram
    %% PawPal+ working UML draft — update in Phase 6 to match the final implementation.

    class Owner {
        +String name
        +List~Pet~ pets
        +addPet(Pet pet)
        +viewAllTasks() List~Task~
    }

    class Pet {
        +String name
        +String species
        +String breed
        +List~Task~ tasks
        +addTask(Task task)
        +getTasks() List~Task~
    }

    class Task {
        +String description
        +Time time
        +int duration
        +Priority priority
        +Frequency frequency
        +boolean completed
        +markComplete()
    }

    class Scheduler {
        +getTasks(Owner owner) List~Task~
        +organizeTasks(List~Task~ tasks) List~Task~
        +generateDailySchedule(Owner owner) List~Task~
    }

    Owner "1" --> "*" Pet : owns
    Pet "1" --> "*" Task : has
    Scheduler ..> Owner : operates on
    Scheduler ..> Pet : reads
    Scheduler ..> Task : organizes
